DTSTAMP:20260310T014016Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260310T181500
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260310T203000
SUMMARY:Trivia at Trailhead (Novato)
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎉 Join Us for Trivia Night! 🧠☕️\nThis event is cross-posted with Sonoma Marin Brat Pack\, Marin County Millennials\, and North Bay 20s30s Meetup\, so RSVPs may not reflect the full crowd.\n\nWe’re Team Quizzards! I’ll be at most events\, and if I can’t make it\, you’ll still find some friendly regulars there. Look for us at the back of the coffee shop — come say hi and join the fun! 🎉\n\n🕡 Trivia kicks off promptly at 6:30 PM\, so swing by a bit earlier if you'd like to grab a drink or something tasty to eat before we get started. I plan to be there at 6 pm to try to get us a good table .\n📍 Location:\nTrailhead Coffee\n127 San Marin Drive\, Novato\, CA\nBring your friends\, your appetite\, and your A-game — see you there! 🙌
