DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T183000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260311T213000
SUMMARY:Redwood Nights - Storytelling Under the Stars @ Deer Park Village 
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nJoin in for an evening of storytelling done under the magical starlit canopy of the Redwoods. This week's theme is "The Moment I finally Chose Myself..."\n\nStories are sometimes poignant\, sometimes hilarious and always true. Featuring storytellers that have appeared on HBO\, PBS\, NPR\, MOTH & more. Complimentary hors d'ouvers and the venue has full bar plus additional wine & beer bar.\n\nEarly Bird tickets are $35 and can be purchased at link below:\n\nhttps://redwoodnightslive.com/storytelling-under-the-stars/\n\nI'll plan to get early to grab seats and we can introduce ourselves before show starts
