SUMMARY:Karaoke Contest
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\n🎤 Mac’s Karaoke Contest 2026\nMac’s is hosting a karaoke contest\, and you can register for free on Eventbrite using the link below. If you plan to actually enter the contest\, I recommend arriving early to make sure your name gets on the list.\nI’m planning to stop by just to observe and enjoy the local talent. Should be a fun night!\nThere are multiple dates scheduled\, so if you can’t make the first one\, the contest will continue over the next few weeks - so be sure to enter the correct date.\nRegister here:\nhttps://www.eventbrite.com/e/macs-karaoke-contest-2026-tickets-1984093772885?aff=ebdssbdestsearch
