DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T223000
SUMMARY:Joose at the Mystic on 3/14
DESCRIPTION:Sonoma-Marin Brat Pack\nIf the raw emotion and dynamic energy of bands like Nirvana\, Pearl Jam\, Smashing Pumpkins\, Foo Fighters\, and other pop-rock classics from the 90s are your jam\, then this where you need to be.\n\nHead on out to the Mystic in Petaluma for a night of making new friends & great music.\n\nThis event probably sell out so buy tickets as soon as you can. See you there\n\nhttps://muhfugginjoose.com/
